WORD
AWARDS 36. Outstanding Comedian – Q. Dube 37. Outstanding Poet – Desire Moyo a.k.a. Moyoxide LITERARY ARTS AWARDS 38. Outstanding Fiction – Novuyo Rosa Tshuma (House of Stones) FASHION
